SYS(3050,1,VAL(SYS(1001)))
*DO TBSAVE.PRG

SET DEFAULT TO W:\FOXAPPS\
OPEN DATABASE W:\FOXAPPS\SHORTDATA SHARED
PUBLIC cMENU

cMENU = "ORDRNTRY" 

** SET ESCAPE OFF **
** DISABLE EXIT HOTKEY **
ON KEY LABEL ESCAPE DO NOESCAPE IN FOXPRO.PRG
ON KEY LABEL ALT+E DO NOEXIT IN FOXPRO.PRG

** SHOW ERROR MESSAGE ON ERRORS **
** ON ERROR DO W:\FOXAPPS\SHRTRIDG\ERR_FIX

** SET DEFAULT SETTINGS **
SET EXCLUSIVE OFF
SET BELL OFF
SET TALK OFF
SET RESOURCE OFF 

KEYBOARD '{ALT+H}'

DO ORDRNTRY\ORDRNTRY.MPR
*READ EVENTS

KEYBOARD '{ALT+H}'   

*SET SKIP OF PAD Hide OF _MSYSMENU .T.

PROCEDURE NOESCAPE
   ESCAPE=""
ENDPROC  

PROCEDURE NOEXIT
	RETURN
ENDPROC 
   











